6. VS Code Tip: Auto Format
->this helps to keep our code clean.
for formatting whole documenting with good indentation
->Launch the command palet by using below short cut 
command palet windows shortcut-> ctrl+shift+p
command palet Mac shortcut    -> cmd+shift+p
->search for format document and click on it.
format document shortcut-> shift+alt+f

alternative
setting->search format-> check format on save

7. List Element
->1. Ordered List   -> <ol> tag defines an ordered list
->2. Unordered List -> <ul> tag defines an unordered (bulleted) list

->3. <li> HTML element
->li-Listed items 
->items in list are wirriten in <li> tags.
->The <li> HTML element is used to represent an item  in a list.

